      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.Item.tcQlonOTpuaKeGLs]{Evolutionist}</p>\n<p>Having managed extraordinary achievements within your niche of transformation, you can afford to specialize into a secondary focus that further refines your powers. Choose one of the following focuses: augmentation, combat, or packmaster. Your focus grants you a basic power at 7th level, an advanced power at 13th level, and an ultimate power at 19th level.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.hmroRe0hkTITCLZQ]{Evolutionary Focus - Augmentation (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.AWFwQoJ0sNVDTOCl]{Evolutionary Focus - Combat}</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.ZIo8qoWjzarBegVC]{Evolutionary Focus - Packmaster}</p>"
